Class Description
ConnectFourGame
The ConnectFourGame class represents a game of connect four - including the board and game state.
GamePiece
Represents a piece in a Connect Four Game.
GamePlayer
Represents a player of a Connect Four Game.
GameState
Represents the state of a Connect Four Game.
GameWinner
Represents the winner of a Connect Four Game.
InvalidMoveExcpetion
Thrown if an invalid move is attempted during a ConnectFourGame.
